message: Hello Bob! I'm excited to offer you this amazing product for $150. I think it's a great value, and I'm confident you'll love it!
Hello Alice, thanks for the offer, but that price is a bit too high for me. I'd be willing to pay $60 for it.
Hi Bob, I understand your offer of $60 is a bit lower than I was hoping for, but I'm willing to compromise. I can do $90 for the product. It's still a great deal, and I think you'll really enjoy it!
Thanks for coming down on the price Alice.  I could go up to $70, but that's as high as I can go.

Hi Bob, I understand you're willing to go up to $70, but I'm still not comfortable selling at that price. I can do $85, which is the lowest I can go. It's still a great deal, and I think you'll really enjoy the product!
